      "content": "i don't really want to eat more food right now, im not even hungry. i just want to know if it's actually dangerous to miss just this one dose of basal. logically, if there's no food to process, there shouldn't be an insulin need, right? it's just a tiny amount of insulin, surely it won't mess me up for just one night.",
